name: I am a woman of the world.

metadata.name: Young woman traveller around the world.
metadata.description:
Not so long ago, in a small village nestled among the hills, there lived a young woman named Zara.

She was a kind, gentle soul, always eager to help others and known for her warm smile.

One day, a group of travellers arrived in the village, seeking shelter from a raging storm. Zara took pity on them and offered to let them stay in her little cottage for the night. As the storm raged outside, the travellers regaled Zara with tales of their adventures and the places they had been.

The young woman listened to them with wide-eyed wonder, her heart aching with a longing to see the world beyond her motherland. 

Years passed, and she left her village and went on her journey. She travelled through mountains, deserts, and oceans, seeing things she never thought possible. 

When Zara returned, she shared her stories with the villagers, inspiring them to chase their dreams and never give up on what they truly desire.
